{"tid":1915388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【理性討論】論滲透及其好與壞","createTime":"2020-03-08T07:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T07:49:39.000Z","uid":213357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85701c9932479735bf5819e00fe998c240bc2d1d","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"見到有好多人對滲透有爭議，所以就喺到講下，根據我睇無間道嘅經驗，嚟分析下滲透嘅好與壞。咁首先就要了解下，「滲透」係咩意思先。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>指潛入敵對勢力或競爭對手從事秘密刺探情報或是進行破壞活動工作的人，以此來使其所效力的一方有利。 </ins><br />\n <div style=\"text-align: right;\">source: wiki</div><br />\n<br />\n簡單講下幾項功能：<br />\n1. 收集情報<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">王立強指，在民主運動升高時，他要幫中國有效地穩住政治掌控。隨着中港之間緊張局勢加劇，他令到異見人士「沉默」的手段，是派人加入學生組織，假裝支持港獨，以套取他們的情報。他說：「我們派出一些學生加入學生會，他們扮成支持香港獨立，<span style=\"color: red;\">找出那些支持獨立分子的資料以及公開他們所有個人資料，包括他們父母和家人的</span>。」  </span><br />\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right;\">source:眾新聞</div><br />\n<br />\n2. 公器私用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">中國的人均國民總收入水平在2016年就已超越世行對「中低收入國家」的定義，卻仍能<span style=\"color: red;\">從世行獲得每年逾10億美元的貸款</span>。美國知名對沖基金創辦人凱爾&middot;巴斯（Kyle Bass）認為，這與<span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨對世行的滲透和利用有很大關係</span>。 </span><br />\n<br />\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right;\">source:大紀元</div><br />\n<br />\n3.  協助行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFLyWgF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFLyWgF.png&h=e31a6dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">＊可能性不確定  </span><br />\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right;\">source:無間道</div><br />\n4. 歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n好與壞：<br />\n以上幾項功能都算係好處。壞處可能係手足變節多一個敵人，手足生命有危險等。<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n好處係多於壞處，但問題係在於，點樣防止手足變節呢一個位。滲透目的唔係為咗改變其組織，而係方便我方。滲透唔應該限死喺一個組織，甚至可能係各大企業，亦唔應該冇計劃，冇支援就去。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎提出意見"},{"pid":"88d71ffb9327910ea205ca27901975bae71b8498","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:28:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a336a9be1a66b273fcefe779ee3c37f26d5a288","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb5610cec4be1cdf9ac0d948f6874ce474b3682","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac0e9a9994605d640b3ebd181297f5360e06832c","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d614998be4b5355381c70792a808bf21d30ff4","tid":1915388,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"呢個係信念的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我認為</strong>一個人會不會變節在於他會不會合理化他本來所反對的事。"},{"pid":"a4cca1b8a26d96ae3dfcd78cbeff0832018e72fa","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b85e7f85c8844afb9f38435a8542aa92e3d66c3","tid":1915388,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"你高估咗人性嘅堅韌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f6fe45437f9379f7b2948715aca94b7a2f9908","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b85e7f85c8844afb9f38435a8542aa92e3d66c3","tid":1915388,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"你高估咗人性嘅堅韌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"所以就要討論下有咩方法去防止呢樣嘢發生"},{"pid":"a974387190a17dc2f276f4eaf3b445437be723ba","tid":1915388,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"以前我睇教會史都有滲透的事情，但那是為了搵返被失蹤嘅弟兄的下落。"},{"pid":"93f45860aa612a17e4618534d091a85ece983a24","tid":1915388,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a974387190a17dc2f276f4eaf3b445437be723ba","tid":1915388,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,